      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i've already talked to my pharmacist and they said it's basically a maintenance thing. i just feel like 5mg is overkill for how healthy i've been feeling. like, if my blood is already working fine, shouldn't a smaller dose be enough to just keep it steady? it feels more logical to scale back if there's no symptoms.",
